# Briefings must pass the publicness sanitizer before they are published.
# Ignore all briefing markdown by default and explicitly un-ignore each
# sanitized, published week, so unsanitized staging briefings (W22-W24 carry
# operator names) cannot reach the public repo or its git history.
# Gate: impact-intel src/render/website/briefing_gate.py
briefings/*.md
!briefings/2026-W19.md
!briefings/2026-W20.md
!briefings/2026-W21.md
